{"tid":2146891,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人呢幾個月咁個時勢仲要辭工","createTime":"2020-08-09T01:31:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T21:04:17.000Z","uid":123613,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0e5c8b7e01aad32ed0b52099a6ff71a514377917","tid":2146891,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T01:31:25.000Z","msg":"上年年中入職 明明in嗰時話去A team 點知去B team<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗住probation後可以過返A (阿head話A team要輪更同啲嘢複雜啲 所以喺B學吓嘢先)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後喺B做到而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> B team唔洗輪更返0830-1800不過係要輪住走24小時e call<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢年幾入面我之後冇一個新人做超過一個月 啲人走得就走 但阿head仲咁喺度加job落我哋條team<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 早兩個月試過有日多e call 加埋office hour啲日常嘢由0530走到0130先收工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只要嗰日係輪e call 可以話係有開工冇收工 上年嗰陣一個月輪5-8日 到上個月開始就10-15日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上個月中開始條team走剩一個 之前可以一個月放3個星期六日 而家就編我放二五 相信要就返阿head同其他senior假期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好在只係捱多一個月 因為有offer 星期五last day 人工多30%最少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"183c73075bc4e8d18ebe46da6b0806148e6db48c","tid":2146891,"uid":104804,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T01:32:59.000Z","msg":"我都想辭<br />\n依家搵緊工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cac56e5d1175ddb6482fc20cbd5ad140dcdc93a","tid":2146891,"uid":112747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T01:46:41.000Z","msg":"本身有積蓄就唔怕la"},{"pid":"7eb83015121aa0e070bfd5a57deda69b71732c3f","tid":2146891,"uid":235911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T02:26:57.000Z","msg":"金融，壓力大，都想裸辭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"748a4476b8b02fb11009fedc436909d8b2c1e61a","tid":2146891,"uid":288764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T02:29:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edbb60ec0f32664ed93e35d51fee6811e09865a8","tid":2146891,"uid":364663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7eb83015121aa0e070bfd5a57deda69b71732c3f","tid":2146891,"uid":235911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T02:26:57.000Z","msg":"金融，壓力大，都想裸辭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T03:12:44.000Z","msg":"做倫敦金？"},{"pid":"6be08d118b9d381d74507705f4386eaa0c7fb9cd","tid":2146891,"uid":235911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"edbb60ec0f32664ed93e35d51fee6811e09865a8","tid":2146891,"uid":364663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7eb83015121aa0e070bfd5a57deda69b71732c3f","tid":2146891,"uid":235911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T02:26:57.000Z","msg":"金融，壓力大，都想裸辭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T03:12:44.000Z","msg":"做倫敦金？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T03:14:49.000Z","msg":"唔係<br />\n正常supporting staff"},{"pid":"8b4df9ff660698a2b26f093774181cfa143257d5","tid":2146891,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T05:43:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b122f7f5710d60a5031b16333565c30af9aafea9","tid":2146891,"uid":296203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T06:21:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe9b13aeb57cb6f02512190f0cd651235249881f","tid":2146891,"uid":185410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T08:58:42.000Z","msg":"7月轉左工<br />\n暫時so far做得幾順利"},{"pid":"b81529a8f2ceb501528e5087bfa9d652f463cc38","tid":2146891,"uid":192558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T21:04:17.000Z","msg":"已祼辭成個月<br />\n工時長，workload大，做到個人勁頹跟住本身好返嘅濕疹又嚴重返又生多幾撻新。<br />\n日日都諗唔知咁辛苦為乜，人工又唔係高，屋企又唔等我開飯，跟住就辭左職。<br />\n<br />\n依家d濕疹好返曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}